  * Add patch from madwifi upstream to fix usage of the pm_message_t type
    on recent kernels (version 2.6.11 and higher), which eliminates some
    compiler warnings, and may make suspend/resume happier with madwifi.
  * Brown paper bag fix: add a missing semicolon in the build-udebs rule.

 -- Adam Conrad <adconrad@ubuntu.com>  Mon, 24 Apr 2006 00:29:32 +1000

