    in NetworkManager 0.6.0, backported to madwifi-old by Johan Kiviniemi.
  * nvidia-glx (but not -legacy) needs to conflict with nvidia-xconfig, as
    we've recently absorbed that binary as well (closes: launchpad.net/6600)

