    - debian/d-i/: Incorporate linux-kernel-restricted-di-2.6 version 0.3.
    - debian/control: Move to debian/control.stub; kernel-wedge will
      generate the real control file.
    - debian/control.stub: Build-depend on kernel-wedge.
    - debian/rules: Update to copy /lib/modules and /lib/hotplug/firmware to
      a temporary tree and generate udebs from them.
